decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kanye-west-bianca-censori-MEGA-GC-Images-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kanye-west-bianca-censori-MEGA-GC-Images-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kanye-west-bianca-censori-MEGA-GC-Images-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kanye-west-bianca-censori-MEGA-GC-Images-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kanye-west-bianca-censori-MEGA-GC-Images-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kanye-west-bianca-censori-MEGA-GC-Images-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·维斯特 (Kanye West)</a>已将“当我在你之前醒来时我想念你”这句话申请了商标——灵感来自于他的妻子比安卡·森索里 (Bianca Censori)。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/kanye-west-white-lives-matter-unforgivable-opinion-3323984">凭借“白人的命也是命”特技，坎耶·维斯特终于到了不归路了吗？</a></li></ul><p>为了庆祝 1 月 6 日妻子的生日，这位备受争议的说唱歌手兼制作人在 Instagram 上分享了一张他的 Censori 的照片，并附上了所需的商标标题：“当我在你之前醒来时，我想念你。”</p><p>据<a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-12966185/Kanye-West-files-trademark-phrase-inspired-wife-Bianca-Censori-BIZARRE-list-goods-services-moisturizers-plush-toys-wireless-receivers-form-jewelry-biological-CLONING.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《每日邮报》</em></a>报道，韦斯特于 1 月 11 日针对该短语提交了九份单独的商标申请，据称该短语被用作推出一系列产品和服务的口号，包括保湿霜、“生物克隆”和毛绒玩具。</p><p>申请中列出的商品和服务范围从技术、科学到时尚，West 的律师 Gregory K. Nelson 确认，他代表他过去提交商标的同一家公司 Ox Paha, Inc. 提交了申请。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C1xJrAgJZkQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); 